" Vim plugin to build a commit file (a text file listing paths to files to
" commit) by recording the file currently being edited into a new or existing
" commit file.
"
" Version:		1.0a
" Maintainer:	Aaron Bieber <aaron@aaronbieber.com>
" License:		??
